# Git Repository Setup

## When to use

- Initializing a new Git repository for Laravel projects or packages
- Setting up branch conventions (main vs 1.x/2.x/3.x)
- Connecting a local repo to GitHub remote
- Configuring initial commit and branch structure for Filament plugins

## Keywords

`git init`, `git setup`, `branch convention`, `git remote`, `repository setup`, `git branch strategy`
